tators'%20gallery%20and%20boxes.%20The%20floodlights%20during%20the%20match%20today%20would%20need%20to%20be%20run%20using%20a%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaipur%20Rural%20Circle%20in-charge%20Ashok%20Khandelwal%20said%20that%20the%20Secretary%20Cricket%20Association%20has%20applied%20to%20increase%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20temporary%20connection%20of%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20temporary%20connection%20is%20200%20KV.%20An%20application%20to%20upgrade%20it%20to%201%20thousand%20KV%20has%20been%20approved%2C%20but%20work%20on%20it%20hasn't%20started%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20there%20was%20an%20uproar%20when%20athletes%20participating%20in%20a%20half-marathon%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20electricity%20supply%20at%20the%20stadium.%20It%20was%20then%20announced%20that%20the%20electricity%20bill%20hadn't%20been%20paid%20since%202009%2C%20and%20had%20gone%20up%20to%20Rs%203.16%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20stadium%2C%20its%20maintenance%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD)%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20expenses%20were%20to%20be%20borne%20by%20the%20Sports%20Department.%20The%20two%20departments%20have%20been%20blaming%20each%20other%20for%20the%20unpaid%20power%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electricity%20company%20sent%20several%20notices%20to%20PWD%20and%20Sports%20Department%20for%20clearance%20of%20dues%2C%20but%20no%20payment%20has%20been%20made%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20international%20cricket%20matches%20have%20been%20organised%20in%20the%20stadium%20since%20the%20power%20connection%20was%20cut%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh%20State%20Cricket%20Sangh%20media%20coordinator%20Tarunesh%20Singh%20Parihar%20said%20they%20are%20skeptical%20about%20hosting%20international%20matches%20as%20there%20will%20be%20a%20problem.%20He%20said%20that%20for%20big%20matches%2C%20they%20use%20generators%20as%20an%20alternative%20arrangement.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20the%20stadium%20lights%20are%20concerned%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20bill%20is%20outstanding%20but%20a%20temporary%20connection%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20the%20name%20of%20CSCS%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parihar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701413040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3sopqa64_raipur-stadium_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-australia-t20-raipur-stadium-no-electricity-at-stadium-hosting-ind-vs-aus-t20-today-bill-not-paid-4623535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fourth%20T20%20international%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20will%20be%20played%20today%20at%20Raipur's%20Shaheed%20Veer%20Narayan%20Singh%20stadium.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-australia-t20-raipur-stadium-no-electricity-at-stadium-hosting-ind-vs-aus-t20-today-bill-not-paid-4623535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-australia-t20-raipur-stadium-no-electricity-at-stadium-hosting-ind-vs-aus-t20-today-bill-not-paid-4623535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-australia-t20-raipur-stadium-no-electricity-at-stadium-hosting-ind-vs-aus-t20-today-bill-not-paid-4623535%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CIA%20Has%20Retrieved%20UFOs%20From%209%20Crash%20Sites%2C%202%20Of%20Them%20Intact%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20(CIA)%20of%20the%20United%20States%20has%20a%20secret%20unit%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Office%20of%20Global%20Access%20(OGA)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20retrieving%20several%20crashed%20UFOs%20(unidentified%20flying%20objects)%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%20At%20least%20nine%20such%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%20craft%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20collected%20by%20the%20agency%20in%20top%20secret%20operations%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said%20in%20its%20report.%20The%20revelations%20are%20based%20on%20the%20accounts%20of%20several%20insiders%20that%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20UFOs%20are%20damaged%20from%20crashes%2C%20at%20least%20two%20are%20intact%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OGA%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20CIA's%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Directorate%2C%20has%20played%20significant%20role%20since%202003%20in%20collection%20of%20aircraft%20believed%20to%20be%20non-human.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-12796167%2FCIA-secret-office-UFO-retrieval-missions-whistleblowers.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDaily%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoke%20to%20were%20directly%20briefed%20by%20people%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20these%20retrieval%20missions.%20One%20of%20them%20said%20that%20the%20US%20intelligence%20agency%20has%20a%20system%20that%20can%20%26quot%3Bdiscern%20UFOs%20that%20are%20cloaked%26quot%3B%20and%20when%20such%20vehicles%20land%20on%20Earth%2C%20special%20military%20units%20are%20sent%20to%20try%20and%20salvage%20the%20wreckage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OGA%20protects%20the%20secrecy%20of%20the%20retrieval%2C%20which%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20US%20military.%20The%20agency%20works%20with%20special%20operations%20forces%20such%20as%20SEAL%20teams%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20missions%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20revelations%20add%20to%20the%20growing%20chorus%20that%20the%20US%20government%20could%20be%20hiding%20advanced%20vehicles%20that%20were%20not%20made%20by%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20this%20year%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20co-sponsored%20a%20bill%20to%20allow%20disclosure%20of%20%26quot%3Brecovered%20technologies%20of%20unknown%20origin%20and%20biological%20evidence%20of%20non-human%20intelligence%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20same%20month%2C%20former%20US%20intelligence%20officer%20David%20Grusch%20had%20gone%20public%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20given%20%26quot%3Bproof%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%20government's%20possession%20of%20alien%20bodies%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20the%20Intelligence%20Community%20(ICIG)%20as%20part%20of%20a%20whistleblower%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20a%20podcast%20last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fex-us-intelligence-office-claims-us-has-variety-of-alien-bodies-4602888%5C%22%3EMr%20Grusch%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20has%20recovered%20multiple%20types%20of%20non-human%20biological%20%26quot%3Bentities%26quot%3B%20from%20crashed%20alien%20aircraft.%20Mr%20Grusch%20is%20an%20Air%20Force%20veteran%20and%20served%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Geospatial%20Intelligence%20Agency%20(NGA)%20and%20the%20National%20Reconnaissance%20Office%20(NRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20US%20government%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvariety%26quot%3B%20of%20alien%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701412740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F7i75c31s_ufo-generic-istock_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcias-secret-office-retrieved-ufos-from-9-crash-sites-around-the-world-report-4623579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20revelations%20add%20to%20the%20growing%20chorus%20that%20the%20US%20government%20could%20be%20hiding%20advanced%20vehicles%20that%20were%20not%20made%20by%20humans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcias-secret-office-retrieved-ufos-from-9-crash-sites-around-the-world-report-4623579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcias-secret-office-retrieved-ufos-from-9-crash-sites-around-the-world-report-4623579%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcias-secret-office-retrieved-ufos-from-9-crash-sites-around-the-world-report-4623579%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Furious%20After%20Airline%20Forces%20Him%20To%20Swap%20Legroom%20Seat%20With%20Couple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20plane%20passenger%20was%20left%20%26quot%3Birritated%20and%20humiliated%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20swap%20his%20extra%20legroom%20seat%20so%20that%20a%20couple%20could%20sit%20next%20to%20each%20other.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EConde%20Nast%20Traveler%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Todd%20Plummer%20was%20travelling%20from%20Istanbul%20to%20Kilimanjaro%20with%20Turkish%20Airlines%20in%20September.%20He%20had%20booked%20a%20normal%20flight%20ticket%20and%20was%20given%2011D%20-%20an%20exit%20row%20seat%20with%20extra%20legroom.%20Being%206%20feet%202%20inches%2C%20Mr%20Plummer%20was%20%26quot%3Bdelighted%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20the%20seat.%20However%2C%20his%20happiness%20was%20short-lived%20as%20he%20was%20soon%20asked%20by%20the%20airlines%20to%20swap%20seats%20with%20a%20couple%20due%20to%20double%20booking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cntraveler.com%2Fstory%2Fdo-airline-seating-systems-favor-couples-over-solo-travelers%5C%22%3ECN%20Traveler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mr%20Plummer%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20sat%20in%20the%20seat%2C%20the%20gate%20agent%20of%20the%20plane%20%26quot%3Bstormed%20up%26quot%3B%20to%20him%20and%20told%20him%20that%20his%20seat%20had%20been%20double%20booked%20with%20a%20couple.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gate%20agent%20said%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20move%20to%209D%20to%20accommodate%20the%20pair%20despite%20being%20settled%20into%20my%20seat%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Plummer%20told%20the%20gate%20agent%20that%20he%20was%20happy%20in%20his%20seat%20and%20would%20prefer%20to%20stay%20there%2C%20however%2C%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20plane%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20full%26quot%3B.%20After%20a%20long%20awkward%20silence%2C%20Mr%20Plummer%20said%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bcaved%26quot%3B%20and%20ended%20up%20moving%20to%20let%20the%20pair%20sit%20next%20to%20each%20other%2C%20rather%20than%20separated%20between%20an%20aisle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20was%20a%20medical%20emergency%20or%20a%20child%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20seated%20with%20their%20parent%2C%20I%20would%20have%20moved%20to%20a%20seat%20of%20equal%20or%20greater%20value%20-%20I'm%20an%20understanding%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Plummer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlas%2C%20for%20over%20seven%20hours%2C%20I%20seethed%20with%20quiet%20rage%20as%20my%20knees%20knocked%20the%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20my%20legs%20cramped%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmatthew-perrys-stepfather-keith-morrison-breaks-silence-1-month-after-actors-death-see-post-4623070%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Perry's%20Stepfather%20Keith%20Morrison%20Breaks%20Silence%201%20Month%20After%20Actor's%20Death.%20See%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20passenger%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20he%20wasn't%20even%20offered%20anything%20as%20thank%20you%20for%20moving%2C%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointing%2C%20irritating%20and%20downright%20humiliating%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20move%20suggested%20that%20couples%20are%20%26quot%3Bmore%20deserving%20of%20a%20superior%20seat%20on%20an%20airplane%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Plummer's%20anger%20over%20this%20incident%20triggered%20a%20debate%20on%20social%20media.%20Several%20inter