gg%20fried%20rice%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20an%20unconfirmed%20story%20of%20how%20Mao%20Anying%20died.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20November%20every%20year%2C%20egg%20fried%20rice%20becomes%20a%20touchy%20subject%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosting%20an%20online%20video%20on%20how%20to%20cook%20the%20dish%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20landed%20Chinese%20celebrity%20chef%20Wang%20Gang%20in%20the%20soup%20with%20the%20country's%20nationalist%20crowd%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20has%202%20million%20YouTube%20subscribers%20and%203.3%20million%20followers%20on%20Weibo.%20On%20Monday%2C%20he%20shared%20a%20seemingly%20innocuous%20cooking%20video%20in%20which%20he%20taught%20viewers%20how%20to%20make%20fried%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20video%20generated%20such%20fierce%20backlash%20online%20that%20Wang%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F3206929472%2FNuMEjy40e%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20an%20apology%20for%20it%20that%20same%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20original%20video%20has%20since%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20never%20make%20fried%20rice%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said%20in%20his%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wang%20Gang%20films%20a%20video%20teaching%20viewers%20how%20to%20prepare%20a%20dish.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6569768847f9ecb37d88f596%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWang%20Gang%20is%20an%20celebrated%20chef%20influencer%20in%20China.%20He%20has%20locked%20comments%20in%20his%20posts%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20Twitter.%3Cp%3EWang%20Gang%2FWeibo%2FScreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20video%20has%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20and%20caused%20a%20terrible%20situation%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20fried%20rice%20is%20a%20touchy%20topic%20in%20late%20November%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offense%20stems%20from%20an%20unsubstantiated%20rumor%20surrounding%20the%20death%20of%20Mao%20Zedong's%20son%2C%20Mao%20Anying%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-blockbuster-battle-at-lake-changjin-box-office-debut-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKorean%20War.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20Mao%20died%20on%20November%2025%20in%201950%20in%20northeastern%20Korea%20while%20serving%20on%20a%20general's%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20retelling%20of%20Mao's%20death%20is%20that%20he%20woke%20up%20late%20that%20day%20and%20missed%20breakfast.%20Per%20the%20story%2C%20he%20stole%20eggs%20from%20the%20camp's%20supplies%20and%20cooked%20himself%20egg%20fried%20rice%20in%20broad%20daylight%20%E2%80%94%20a%20violation%20of%20army%20rules%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20from%20his%20breakfast%20supposedly%20gave%20away%20his%20position%20to%20US%20forces%2C%20who%20killed%20Mao%20in%20a%20napalm%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20never%20confirmed%2C%20the%20story%20has%20become%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20criticism%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20in%20China%2C%20and%20subsequently%20an%20intensely%20sensitive%20subject%20among%20party%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20celebrate%20November%2025%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2F2021%2F10%2Fnetizen-voices-no-egg-fried-rice-allowed-in-october-or-november%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaving%20grace%20from%20a%20potential%20Mao%20dynasty%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20China%2C%20which%20could%20have%20birthed%20a%20nation%20ruled%20by%20one%20family%20like%20in%20North%20Korea.%20Critics%20of%20the%20Mao%20regime%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epost%20photos%20of%20egg%20fried%20rice%20or%20make%20a%20point%20to%20eat%20the%20dish%20on%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20and%20its%20most%20ardent%20supporters%20thus%20view%20the%20mentioning%20of%20egg%20fried%20rice%20during%20this%20period%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%2C%20and%20mete%20out%20criticism%20or%20punishment%20to%20those%20who%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Weibo%20account%20of%20the%20Jiangsu%20branch%20of%20China%20Unicom%2C%20a%20telco%20giant%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fenglish%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Frice-10262021092548.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20posted%20a%20recipe%20for%20egg%20fried%20rice%20on%20October%2024%2C%20Mao's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Nanchang%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fmeiti%2Fql2-10122021071401.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetained%20by%20police%20for%2010%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20posting%20online%20that%20egg%20fried%20rice%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20success%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Korean%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20third%20offense%20for%20Wang%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Wang%2C%20the%20influencer%20chef%20is%20on%20his%20third%20strike%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20ill-timed%20egg%20fried%20rice%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20channel%20released%20an%20egg%20fried%20rice%20recipe%20on%20October%2022%2C%202018%2C%20two%20days%20before%20Mao's%20birthday%2C%20and%20on%20October%2024%2C%202020%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2F702659.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20Digital%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20US-based%20501(c)(3)%20organization%20that%20documents%20internet%20censorship%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20was%20criticized%20both%20times%2C%20and%20apologized%20for%20the%20apparent%20gaffe%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20state%20media%20outlet%20People's%20Daily%20shared%20his%20fried%20rice%20recipe%20in%202018%20before%20the%20backlash%20began%2C%20per%20China%20Digital%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20nationalist%20social%20media%20users%20in%20China%20say%20Wang%20is%20clearly%20displaying%20a%20pattern%20of%20trying%20to%20stir%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWang%20Gang%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20cook.%20He%20is%20very%20familiar%20with%20internet%20memes%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6191604322%2FNuDKh5MaM%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20blogger%20wrote.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1298124720%2FNuMbV2Ttx%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20blogger%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20Wang%20of%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%20enjoying%20himself%26quot%3B%20despite%20his%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20so%20much%20time%20in%20a%20year%20to%20make%20fried%20rice%2C%20but%20he%20has%20to%20rush%20to%20do%20it%20on%20Anying's%20birthday%20or%20death%20anniversary%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1686096655%2FNuOnidilV%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyet%20another%20blogger.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20risen%20to%20Wang's%20defense%2C%20saying%20his%20videos%20are%20receiving%20undue%20scrutiny.%20Notably%2C%20his%20egg%20fried%20rice%20recipe%20wasn't%20posted%20on%20Mao's%20death%20anniversary%20of%20November%2025%2C%20but%20two%20days%20later%2C%20on%20November%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20looked%20at%20his%20channel.%20Wang%20Gang%20makes%20egg%20fried%20rice%20over%20several%20months%20a%20year.%20Why%20do%20you%20choose%20to%20stare%20at%20them%20for%20just%20these%20few%20days%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20on%20which%20exact%20days%20is%20eating%20egg%20fried%20rice%20not%20allowed%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20questioned.%20%26quot%3BDo%20ordinary%20folk%20eating%20egg%20fried%20rice%20have%20to%20skip%20a%20day%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-china-egg-fried-rice-mao-zedong-son-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701412493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656974e958e7c0c29a2897f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-china-egg-fried-rice-mao-zedong-son-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Internet%20celebrity%20chef%20Wang%20Gang%20is%20for%20the%20third%20time%20facing%20backlash%20over%20posting%20an%20egg%20fried%20rice%20tutorial%20at%20an%20inopportune%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-china-egg-fried-rice-mao-zedong-son-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20wants%20to%20work%20with%20THESE%20directors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701412226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105647201%2Cimgsize-21094.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-reveals-his-wish-to-work-with-these-directors%2Farticleshow%2F105647201.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105647201.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%20responded%20to%20the%20many%20questions%20from%20his%20personal%20and%20professional%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-reveals-his-wish-to-work-with-these-directors%2Farticleshow%2F105647201.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22