om%2C%20charges%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20scavenged%20for%20scraps%20in%20nearby%20restaurant%20dumpsters%20and%20was%20beaten%20with%20electrical%20wire%2C%20PVC%20pipe%2C%20metal%20rods%2C%20wooden%20boards%2C%20sticks%20and%20a%20water%20supply%20hose%20for%20a%20washing%20machine%2C%20St%20Louis%20Post-Dispatch%2C%20a%20major%20regional%20newspaper%2C%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20absolutely%20inhumane%20and%20unconscionable%20that%20one%20human%20being%20could%20treat%20another%20human%20being%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20McCulloch%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20defendants%20are%20accused%20of%20confining%20and%20abusing%20the%20victim%20at%20three%20different%20homes%20owned%20by%20Sattaru%20in%20Defiance%2C%20Dardenne%20Prairie%20and%20O'Fallon%2C%20starting%20in%20April%202023%2C%20according%20to%20St%20Charles%20County's%20official%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESattaru%20was%20identified%20by%20investigators%20as%20the%20ringleader%20and%20lives%20in%20the%20O'Fallon%20home%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suspect%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Sattaru%2C%2035%2C%20is%20additionally%20charged%20with%20human%20trafficking%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20slavery%20and%20contributing%20to%20human%20trafficking%20through%20misuse%20of%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPenumetcha%20and%20Penmatsa%20live%20in%20the%20home%20where%20the%20student%20was%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20the%20student%20had%20come%20to%20the%20US%20from%20India%20last%20year%20with%20hopes%20of%20studying%20at%20Missouri%20University%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20in%20Rolla.%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20Sattaru's%20homes%20beginning%20in%20April%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20begin%20chores%20around%204%3A30%20am%2C%20work%20a%20full%20day%20for%20Sattaru's%20IT%20company%20and%20then%20complete%20a%20list%20of%20evening%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20told%20police%20he%20regularly%20got%20three%20hours%20of%20sleep%20on%20a%20concrete%20floor%20in%20a%20locked%20basement%20where%20Sattaru%20monitored%20him%20with%20a%20surveillance%20camera%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%2020-year-old%20didn't%20complete%20the%20tasks%20properly%2C%20he%20was%20severely%20beaten.%20Charges%20say%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20strip%20down%20naked%20and%20was%20hit%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20He%20was%20kicked%2C%20stomped%20and%20lashed%2C%20charges%20say%2C%20and%20his%20injuries%20included%20previous%20fractures%20and%20breaks%20that%20did%20not%20heal%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20answered%20the%20door%20at%20Sattaru's%20home%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20None%20of%20the%20three%20men%20had%20attorneys%20listed%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20beat%20him%20with%20their%20fists%2C%20they%20stomped%20on%20him%2C%20they%20beat%20him%20with%20electrical%20wiring%2C%20with%20PVC%20pipes%2C%E2%80%9D%20McCulloch%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20forced%20him%20to%20sleep%20in%20an%20unfinished%20basement%2C%20they%20starved%20him%2C%20and%20limited%20his%20access%20to%20the%20public%20and%20to%20restrooms.%E2%80%9D%20McCulloch%20commended%20that%20citizen%20for%20making%20the%20rescue%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20see%20something%2C%20say%20something.%20We%20would%20much%20rather%20check%20it%20out%20and%20find%20nothing%20than%20have%20an%20incident%20like%20this%20that's%20been%20going%20on%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20McCulloch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20three%20suspects%20are%20wealthy%20and%20have%20political%20connections%20in%20India%2C%20McCulloch%20said%20they%20are%20being%20held%20at%20the%20St.%20Charles%20County%20Jail%20without%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbours%20in%20O'Fallon%20were%20shaken%20by%20the%20arrests%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20said%20they'd%20had%20pleasant%20interactions%20with%20the%20family%2C%20waving%20as%20they%20passed%20on%20the%20street%20or%20playing%20with%20children%20in%20the%20cul-de-sac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20shocking%2C%20for%20sure%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chirag%20Shah%2C%20who%20lives%20down%20the%20street%20from%20Sattaru's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Defiance%2C%20an%20unincorporated%20community%20of%20less%20than%20100%20people%20known%20for%20its%20wineries%2C%20gift%20shops%20and%20position%20along%20the%20Katy%20Trail%2C%20neighbours%20watched%20as%20police%20flocked%20to%20the%20home%20beginning%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20were%20told%20at%20first%20by%20a%20man%20in%20the%20home%20that%20they%20couldn't%20come%20inside%2C%20but%20the%2020-year-old%20eventually%20came%20running%20from%20the%20basement.%20He%20was%20trembling%20uncontrollably%2C%20heavily%20scarred%20and%20suffering%20from%20bruising%20and%20swelling%20all%20over%20his%20body%2C%20charges%20say.%20PTI%20NSA%20AKJ%20NSA%20NSA%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701411960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F3eb3kf1_us-police-generic_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2F3-arrested-for-beating-indian-student-forcing-him-into-labour-for-months-in-us-4623489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20in%20the%20US%20have%20rescued%20a%2020-year-old%20Indian%20student%2C%20who%20was%20held%20captive%20for%20months%20without%20access%20to%20a%20bathroom%2C%20viciously%20beaten%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20work%20at%20three%20homes%20by%20his%20cousin%20and%20two%20other%20men.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2F