.com%2Farticleshow%2F105637134.cms%3Futm_source%3Dcontentofinterest%26utm_medium%3Dtext%26utm_campaign%3Dcppst%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20by%3Cem%3E%20The%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20telling%20them%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Caround%2019-20%20minor%20to%20medium%C2%A0level%20collapses%20occurred%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20incidents%20happen%20during%20every%20tunnel%20construction%20project%20but%20we%20were%20unlucky%20this%20time%20as%20workers%20got%20trapped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20big-ticket%20Char%20Dham%20route%20in%20the%20fragile%20Himalayan%20eco-zone%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20all-weather%20roads%20between%20four%20important%20Hindu%20pilgrim%20sites%2C%20the%20Gangotri%2C%20Yamunotri%2C%20Kedarnath%20and%20Badrinath%20shrines%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20cites%20another%20official%20connected%20with%20the%20tunnel%20construction%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cpreferring%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20tunnel%20had%20faced%20numerous%20cavity%20collapses%20due%20to%20the%20challenging%20geology%20of%20the%20region%20and%20significant%20rock%20deformation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20what%20is%20likely%20to%20add%20to%20already%20existing%20concerns%20about%20no%20%E2%80%98Environment%20Assessment%20Impact%E2%80%99%20study%20having%20been%20done%20for%20this%20important%20project%2C%20the%20news%20report%20quotes%20how%20Bernard%20Gruppe%2C%20the%20European%20company%20%E2%80%9Cproviding%20design%20services%20to%20Navayuga%20Engineering%2C%20the%20construction%20firm%20that%20has%20got%20the%20contract%20for%20the%20tunnel%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgeological%20conditions%20(at%20the%20tunnel%20site)%20proved%20to%20be%20more%20challenging%20than%20predicted%20in%20the%20tender%20documents%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20experts%20turned%20up%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-collapse-no-show-by-central-team-on-safety-mission-for-construction-restart%2Fcid%2F1983750%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20about%20the%20no-show%20of%20a%20team%20of%20experts%20from%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20expected%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20collapsed%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20on%20Thursday%20to%20review%20how%20safe%20it%20was%20before%20the%20resumption%20of%20construction.%E2%80%9D%20Uttarakhand%20government%20officials%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20did%20not%20arrive.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Uttarakhand%20government%20official%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20asked%20to%20be%20at%20the%20spot%20to%20receive%20them%20but%20the%20team%20didn%E2%80%99t%20arrive.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20there%20was%20no%20information%20when%20the%20team%20might%20turn%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20there%20was%20no%20clarity%20over%20the%20central%20team%E2%80%99s%20arrival%2C%20officials%20of%20the%20private%20engineering%20firm%20with%20the%20contract%20for%20the%20tunnel%20project%20%E2%80%9Csounded%20confident%20about%20resuming%20work%20soon.%E2%80%9D%20A%20company%20official%20involved%20in%20the%20project%20told%20reporters%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20work%20with%20doubled%20enthusiasm%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20tunnel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20have%20boosted%20our%20morale.%20We%20will%20complete%20the%20project%20before%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20recalls%20that%20V.K.%20Singh%2C%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20road%20transport%20and%20highways%2C%20had%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20of%20experts%20would%20carry%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20audit%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20project%2C%20but%20had%20not%20specified%20a%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBackstory%3A%20Back%20in%20the%20Tunnel%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-warning-environment-development%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20earlier%2C%20in%202013%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20decided%20to%20waive%20environmental%20clearances%20for%20road%20projects%20less%20than%20100%20km%20long.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20the%20NDA%20made%20use%20of%20this%20waiver%20even%20though%20the%20Main%20Himalayan%20Thrust%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20Indian%20plate%20pushes%20under%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20runs%20through%20Uttarakhand%20but%20comes%20close%20to%20the%20tunnel%20site.%20This%2C%20as%20activist%20Himanshu%20Thakkar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fopinion%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-collapse-at-what-point-will-we-wake-up-to-the-himalayan-disasters-11793081.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20creates%20obvious%20%E2%80%9Cseismic%20and%20shear%20zone%20implications%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20no%20room%20for%20their%20concerns%20in%20this%20abbreviated%20planning%20process%2C%20locals%20approached%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-n