was%20counting%20two%20Russian-Israeli%20women%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20part%20of%20the%20seventh%20batch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20brought%20relief%20for%20Keren%20Shem%2C%20whose%20daughter%20Mia%20was%20among%20those%20freed.%20The%20family%20released%20footage%20showing%20Keren%20weeping%20with%20joy%20as%20she%20was%20informed%20by%20phone%20of%20her%20daughter's%20imminent%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMia%20is%20coming%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20cried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20the%20hostages%20arrived%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20country's%20prison%20service%20said%20another%2030%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20--%2023%20minors%20and%20seven%20women%20--%20had%20been%20freed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20leaders%20in%20Israel%20and%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20Blinken%20said%20Washington%20wants%20%26quot%3Bto%20see%20this%20process%20continue%20to%20move%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20an%20eighth%20day%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20Hamas%20said%20the%20group%20backed%20another%20extension%20and%20mediators%20were%20working%20to%20prolong%20the%20pause%2C%20but%20the%20negotiations%20appeared%20to%20have%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20made%20it%20clear%20it%20viewed%20the%20truce%20as%20a%20temporary%20pause%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20swore...%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20and%20nothing%20will%20stop%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20released%20by%20his%20office%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20Blinken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20government%20has%20come%20under%20increasing%20pressure%2C%20however%2C%20to%20account%20for%20how%20it%20will%20protect%20civilians%20in%20the%20territory%2C%20which%20is%20under%20blockade%2C%20with%20no%20way%20for%20people%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinken%20war