ention%20a%20specific%20date%2C%20but%20had%20clearly%20laid%20out%20how%20Hamas%20would%20come%20past%20the%20border%20and%20carry%20out%20the%20attack.%20The%20plan%20which%20was%20dismissed%20as%20too%20ambitious%2C%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20deadliest%20day%20in%20the%2075-year-old%20Israeli-Palestine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%2C200%20Israelis%20were%20killed%20and%20over%20200%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20when%20they%20launched%20an%20offensive%20on%20October%207.%20Since%20then%2C%20Israel%20has%20put%20Gaza's%20population%20of%202.3%20million%20under%20siege%20and%20conducted%20aerial%20bombardments%20and%20ground%20raids.%20Gaza%20health%20officials%2C%20considered%20reliable%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20say%20about%2011%2C500%20Palestinians%20are%20confirmed%20killed%2C%20around%2040%25%20of%20them%20children%2C%20and%20more%20are%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20report%20said%20that%20Israel%20intelligence%20had%20prepared%20a%2040-page%20document%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20codenamed%20it%20'Jericho%20Wall'.%20The%20document%20clearly%20stated%20how%20Hamas%20would%20overrun%20bases%2C%20target%20critical%20infrastructure%20and%20take%20hostages.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20followed%20the%20blueprint%20with%20shocking%20precision%2C%20and%20started%20by%20firing%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20at%20Israel.%20They%20then%20used%20drones%20to%20knock%20out%20at%20the%20cameras%20at%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20border.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20their%20operatives%20streaming%20into%20Southern%20Israel%20towns%20using%20motorcyles%2C%20paragliders%20and%20boats%2C%20just%20as%20the%20'Jericho%20Wall'%20document%20had%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20after%20the%20attack%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20only%20temporarily%20stopped%20its%20raids%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Qatar%20mediated%20a%20truce.%20Both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20release%20some%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20for%20ceasefire.%20The%20truce%20has%20also%20allowed%20some%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20Gaza%20after%20much%20of%20the%20coastal%20territory%20was%20reduced%20to%20wasteland%20in%20the%20Israeli%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20made%20clear%20it%20sees%20the%20truce%20as%20a%20temporary%20pause%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20and%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20resume%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20swore...%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20and%20nothing%20will%20stop%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20released%20by%20his%20office%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701409620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fresqt0ok_israel-hamas-attack-afp_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-knew-of-hamas-oct-7-plan-dismissed-it-as-too-ambitious-report-4623338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20military%20leaders%20had%20obtained%20detailed%20documents%20on%20Hamas%20battle%20plans%20for%20October%207%2C%20but%20did%20not%20pay%20any%20heed%20to%20them%20as%20they%20thought%20the%20plan%20was%20far-fetched%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-knew-of-hamas-oct-7-plan-dismissed-it-as-too-ambitious-report-4623338%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-knew-of-hamas-oct-7-plan-dismissed-it-as-too-ambitious-report-4623338%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-knew-of-hamas-oct-7-plan-dismissed-it-as-too-ambitious-report-4623338%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Saw%20a%20Very%20Polluted%20November%20With%20Average%20AQI%20at%20372%22%2C%22conte