%2Fbarclays-citi-raise-indias-economic-growth-closer-to-7-after-gdp-boost%2Farticleshow%2F105644371.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%20Jailed%20After%20Dumping%20Pregnant%20Girlfriend's%20Dead%20Body%20On%20Highway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2033-year-old%20man%20in%20the%20US%20who%20was%20caught%20on%20video%20dumping%20his%20pregnant%20girlfriend's%20dead%20body%20on%20the%20side%20of%20an%20expressway%20in%20New%20York%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2025%20years%20to%20life%20in%20prison%20for%20the%20killing.%20According%20to%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Goey%20Charles%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20in%20November%20of%20one%20count%20of%20second-degree%20murder%20in%20the%20October%202020%20killing%20of%2029-year-old%20Vanessa%20Pierre.%20He%20was%20arrested%203%20days%20after%20Ms%20Pierre's%20body%20was%20found%20on%20Horace%20Harding%20Expressway%20in%20Bayside%2C%20Queens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20asked%20for%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20because%20of%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20crime%20and%20the%20defendant's%20remorseless%20discarding%20of%20the%20lifeless%20body%20of%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20was%20soon%20to%20be%20the%20mother%20of%20his%20child.%20The%20sentence%20does%20not%20bring%20Vanessa%20back%2C%20but%20it%20achieves%20justice%20in%20her%20memory%2C%26quot%3B%20Queens%20District%20Attorney%20Melina%20Katz%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqueensda.org%2Flong-island-man-sentenced-for-murder-of-pregnant-girlfriend%2F%5C%22%3Erelease%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F29%2Fmetro%2Fny-man-who-strangled-pregnant-girlfriend-sentenced-to-25-years%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Goey%20Charles'%20conviction%20came%20after%20surveillance%20footage%20showed%20him%20dragging%20Ms%20Pierre's%20lifeless%20bo