F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNothing%20In%20Offing%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20Says%20No%20Plans%20To%20Set%20Up%208th%20Pay%20Commission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20the%20eighth%20Pay%20Commission%20for%20some%205.4%20million%20central%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election%20next%20year%2C%20Finance%20Secretary%20TV%20Somanathan%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20in%20the%20offing%20regarding%20setting%20up%20the%208th%20Pay%20Commission.%20It's%20not%20due%20at%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanathan%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20elections%2C%20governments%20have%20used%20the%20establishing%20or%20implementation%20of%20the%20Pay%20Commission%20as%20an%20effective%20tool%20to%20win%20over%20central%20government%20employees%2C%20armed%20forces%20personnel%20and%20family%20pensioners.%20The%207th%20Pay%20Commission%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20in%20September%202013%2C%20months%20before%20state%20and%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20steered%20clear%20of%20such%20a%20move%2C%20instead%20focusing%20on%20a%20review%20of%20a%20new%20pension%20scheme%20that%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20for%20new%20state%20and%20central%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20scheme%2C%20employees%20contribute%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20basic%20salary%2C%20while%20the%20government%20pays%2014%25.%20It%20has%20become%20politically%20contentious%2C%20with%20several%20opposition-ruled%20states%20switching%20to%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20that%20guarantees%20pensioners%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20last%20drawn%20salary%20monthly%2C%20without%20any%20employee%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20led%20by%20the%20Finance%20Secretary%20to%20review%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20completed%20consultations%20with%20all%20concerned%20and%20our%20report%20should%20be%20submitted%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20may%20bring%20about%20changes%20to%20ensure%20employees%20get%20at%20least%2040%20to%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20last%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20looming%2C%20there%20is%20increasing%20political%20pressure%20on%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20to%20announce%20and%20notify%20the%208th%20pay%20commission%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20results%20of%20elections%20in%20five%20states.%20State%20poll%20results%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20are%20widely%20seen%20to%20be%20the%20semi-final%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20national%20election%2C%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20seek%20a%20third%20straight%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701406320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fhfvgc2h4_money-generic_625x300_20_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-secretary-tv-somanathan-says-no-plan-yet-to-set-up-eighth-pay-commission-4623188%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20the%20eighth%20Pay%20Commission%20for%20some%205.4%20million%20central%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election%20next%20year%2C%20Finance%20Secretary%20TV%20Somanathan%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-secretary-tv-somanathan-says-no-plan-yet-to-set-up-eighth-pay-commission-4623188%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-secretary-tv-somanathan-says-no-plan-yet-to-set-up-eighth-pay-commission-4623188%2Famp%2F1