l%20Lamb...%26quot%3B%3A%20New%20Pakistan%20Captain%20Told.%20His%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20cricket%20is%20embarking%20on%20a%20new%20journey%20starting%20with%20their%20Australia%20Tour%2C%20that%20starts%20with%20Test%20on%20December%2014.%20After%20a%20disappointing%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20campaign%2C%20Pakistan%20cricket%20saw%20many%20changes.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20resigned%20as%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20captain.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shan%20Masood%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1483-shan-masood-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShan%20Masood%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20appointed%20the%20Pakistan%20Test%20team's%20skipper%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shaheen%20Afridi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108785-shaheen-afridi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShaheen%20Afridi%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20T20I%20team.%20Several%20officials%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20selection%20committee%20were%20also%20changed.%20How%20the%20experiment%20will%20bear%20fruit%20will%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20intrigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20new%20Test%20captain%20Shan%20Masood%20was%20recently%20asked%20on%20whether%20he%20might%20be%20made%20the%20proverbial%20'sacrificial%20lamb'%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAapko%20Qurbani%20ka%20bakra%20banaya%20jayega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(You%20will%20be%20made%20the%20sacrificial%20lamb)%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20reporter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWrmPgURfX_o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Shan%20Masood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20we%20see%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity.%20When%20you%20haven't%20done%20something%20before%20in%20your%20history%2C%20then%20you%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20try%20to%20change%20it.%20So%20that's%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20to%20get%20a%20positive%20result%20for%20Pakistan%20and%20in%20this%20World%20Test%20Championship%2C%26quot%3B%20Shan%20Masood%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20far%20as%20being%20%3Cem%3Equrbaani%20ka%20bakra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sacrificial%20lamb)%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20captaincy%2C%20playing%20as%20a%20player%20in%20the%20side%2C%20these%20are%20all%20temporary%20things%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20are%20in%20that%20place%2C%20or%20seat%2C%20you%20should%20relish%20the%20opportunity%2C%20enjoy%20it%20and%20try%20and%20take%20responsibility%2C%20and%20give%20your%20best%20ability%20to%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Test%20captain%20Shan%20Masood's%20contract%20was%20on%20Thursday%20upgraded%20to%20'B'%20category%20from%20earlier%20'D'%20by%20the%20country's%20cricket%20board%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20team%20led%20by%20him%20left%20for%20Australia%20for%20a%20Test%20series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20Masood%20was%20named%20Test%20captain%20on%20November%2015%20until%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%202023-25%20cycle%2C%20after%20Babar%20Azam%20stepped%20down%2C%20following%20Pakistan's%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20debacle%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20has%20decided%20to%20upgrade%20Pakistan%20Test%20captain%20Shan%20Masood's%20category%20in%20the%20central%20contract%20list%20from%20D%20to%20B%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PCB%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20in%20line%20with%20board's%20policy%20that%20if%20a%20centrally%20contracted%20player%20below%20A%20or%20B%20categories%20is%20appointed%20captain%2C%20their%20contract%20shall%20be%20upgraded%20to%20category%20B%20for%20the%20tenure%20of%20their%20captaincy.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-handed%20batter%20has%20featured%20in%2030%20Tests%2C%20amassing%201%2C597%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20left%20for%20Australia%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-match%20Test%20series%20against%20Australia%20begins%20on%20December%2014%20in%20Perth.%20The%20team%20will%20play%20a%20tour%20match%20against%20Australian%20PM%20XI%20from%20December%206-9%20in%20Canberra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701403740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2Fh8697rcg_shan-masood-twitter_625x300_08_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyou-will-be-made-sacrificial-lamb-new-pakistan-test-captain-shan-masood-told-his-reply-is-4622263%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20disappointing%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20campaign%2C%20Pakistan%20cricket%20saw%20many%20changes%20with%20new%20captains%20being%20appointed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyou-will-be-made-sacrificial-lamb-new-pakistan-test-captain-shan-masood-told-his-reply-is-4622263%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyou-will-be-made-sacrificial-lamb-new-pakistan-test-captain-shan-masood-told-his-reply-is-4622263%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyou-will-be-made-sacrificial-lamb-new-pakistan-test-captain-shan-masood-told-his-reply-is-4622263%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NIT%20Srinagar%20Closed%20Amid%20Protests%20Over%20Online%20Post%2C%20Other%20Colleges%20Shut%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(NIT)%20in%20Srinagar%20has%20been%20closed%20and%20the%20students%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20campus%20and%20the%20hostel%20amid%20tensions%20over%20an%20alleged%20blasphemous%20post%20by%20a%20non-local%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20degree%20colleges%20across%20Kashmir%20too%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20begin%20online%20classes%20from%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20students%20(boys%20and%20girls)%20are%20directed%20to%20leave%20the%20campus%2F%20hostel%20by%20or%20before%2010%20am%20tomorrow%20on%20December%201%2C2023%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Dean%2C%20Students%20Welfare%2C%20NIT.%20The%20mess%20service%20in%20the%20campus%20too%20will%20be%20suspended%20from%20breakfast%20onwards%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20cited%20%26quot%3Bearly%20onset%20of%20winter%26quot%3B%20for%20suspending%20physical%20classes%20in%20colleges%20even%20as%20high%20schools%20and%20higher%20secondary%20schools%20continue%20to%20remain%20open%20for%20regular%20classes%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20non-local%20NIT%20student%20posted%20an%20alleged%20blasphemous%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20triggering%20massive%20protests%20in%20the%20institute.%20Hundreds%20of%20students%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20and%20demanded%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20protests%20spread%20to%20other%20colleges%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIT%20campus%20is%20currently%20under%20heavy%20security%20cover%20and%20academic%20activities%20suspended%20to%20curb%20further%20protests.%20The%20accused%20has%20been%20charged%20for%20hurting%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20a%20particular%20community%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20provision%20is%20also%20being%20introduced%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procdure%20(CrPC)%20to%20curb%20the%20use%20of%20social%20media%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20communal%20disharmony%2C%20according%20to%20Rashmi%20Ranjan%20Swain%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20post%20videos%2C%20including%20those%20aimed%20at%20disrespecting%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20and%20those%20who%20forward%20it%20will%20be%20committing%20a%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Swain.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20144%20CrPC%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20on%20the%20posting%20of%20any%20type%20of%20content%20-%20message%2C%20video%2C%20audio%20-%20which%20will%20spread%20communal%20disharmony%20and%20terrorise%20or%20threaten%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20it%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incident%20at%20NIT%20and%20charged%20the%20student%20for%20posting%20sensitive%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident%20of%20uploading%20of%20sensitive%20content%20against%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20by%20one%20student%20of%20NIT%20Srinagar.%20Upon%20receipt%20of%20communication%20from%20NIT%20authorities%2C%20case%20FIR%20No.156%2F23%20u%2Fs%20295A%2C153A%2C153%20IPC%20registered%20in%20PS%20Nigeen%20on%2028.11.23%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Srinagar%20Police%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommon%20public%20is%20appealed%20to%20desist%20from%20spreading%20rumours%2Ffalse%20information.%20They%20shouldn't%20fall%20prey%20to%20false%20propaganda%20of%20anti-social%20elements.%20Legal%20action%20shall%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20are%20found%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20provocative%20act%2Finstigation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701403620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fm014j6gg_nit-srinagar-facebook-650_625x300_04_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnit-srinagar-closed-amid-protests-over-online-post-other-colleges-shut-too-4622806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(NIT)%20in%20Srinagar%20has%20been%20closed%20and%20t