%20has%20the%20role%20of%20administering%20the%20UN%20body%20and%20appointing%20the%20director-general.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20three%20constitutional%20organs%20of%20UNESCO%2C%20along%20with%20the%20194-member%20general%20conference%20and%20the%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20board%20chair%2C%20there%20are%20six%20vice-chairs%20representing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unesco.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fmedias%2Ffichiers%2F2023%2F11%2Fmembers-electoral-group_2023-2025_en.pdf%5C%22%3Esix%20regional%20or%20electoral%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20which%20all%20member%20states%20are%20categorised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20permanent%20mission%20to%20UNESCO%20is%20led%20by%20the%20only%20political%20appointee%20to%20currently%20head%20an%20Indian%20diplomatic%20mission.%20Vishal%20V.%20Sharma%20was%20appointed%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20permanent%20representative%20(PR)%20to%20the%20UN%20cultural%20body%20in%20October%202020%20for%20a%20three%20year-term.%20He%20got%20a%20one-year%20extension%20on%20his%20term%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20appointment%20as%20permanent%20representative%2C%20Sharma%20had%20been%20known%20as%20an%20aide%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Gujarat.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2FA%2520communication%2520specialist%2520in%2520the%2520BJP%2C%2520Sharma%2520had%2520been%2520officer%2520on%2520special%2520duty%2520in%2520the%2520early%2520years%2520of%2520the%2520Modi%2520regime%2520when%2520he%2520was%2520the%2520Gujarat%2520chief%2520minister.%5C%22%3EHis%20official%20UNESCO%20bio%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20he%20had%20served%20as%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20to%20Modi%20during%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20term%20as%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister.%20He%20gained%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20notoriety%20for%20calling%20Modi%20a%20%E2%80%98supercomputer%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fvishal-sharma-india-unesco-ambassador%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20at%20time%20of%20his%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20selection%20had%20been%20a%20surprise%20since%20the%20post%20of%20Indian%20PR%20to%20UNESCO%20had%20earlier%20been%20filled%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20or%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbandoned%20by%20Global%20South%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20the%20defeat%20margin%20is%20conspicuous%2C%20given%20India%E2%80%99s%20historical%20success%20in%20securing%20positions%20when%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20roles%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20other%20multilateral%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20UNESCO%20rules%20of%20procedure%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20consensus%20regarding%20vice-chairs%20of%20the%20Board%2C%20then%20the%20election%20is%20held%20by%20secret%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformed%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20voting%20amount%20indicated%20that%20while%20India%20did%20get%20most%20of%20its%20votes%20from%20the%20Western%20bloc%2C%20most%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20from%20Asia%2C%20Africa%2C%20Arab%20and%20Latin%20American%20electoral%20groups%20seemed%20to%20have%20voted%20for%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UNESCO%20Executive%20Board%2C%20there%20are%2017%20countries%20from%20the%20Western%20and%20eastern%20European%20groups%2C%20while%20the%20other%2042%20members%20are%20divided%20among%20the%20four%20remaining%20electoral%20groups%20and%20broadly%20constitute%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defeat%20is%20especially%20galling%20as%20India%20has%20been%20consistently%20projecting%20itself%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20especially%20during%20its%20G20%20presidency.%20It%20organised%20two%20virtual%20%E2%80%98Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%20summits%20during%20this%20year%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20issues%20raised%20would%20contribute%20to%20the%20G20%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20G20%20summits%2C%20there%20were%20numerous%20posters%20on%20the%20roads%20of%20the%20Indian%20capital%20with%20the%20photo%20of%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%2C%20alongside%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CGiving%20Voice%20to%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20approach%20to%20UN%20contests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20well-versed%20in%20multilateral%20diplomacy%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20filling%20posts%20at%20the%20UN%20which%20are%20reserved%20on%20geographical%20distribution%20and%20aligned%20with%20regional%20groups%20typically%20undergo%20a%20two-stage%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20regional%20group%20usually%20takes%20a%20decision%20among%20itself%20to%20find%20a%20consensus%20candidate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20effort%20at%20this%20stage%20is%20to%20persuade%20the%20regional%20members%20to%20only%20back%20the%20Indian%20candidate%20or%20to%20persuade%20others%20to%20withdraw.%20States%20may%20withdraw%20if%20they%20sense%20that%20they%20will%20not%20get%20votes%20for%20victory%2C%20which%20we%20would%20also%20do%20if%20we%20felt%20similarly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%2C%20then%20an%20assessment%20is%20made%20again%20based%20on%20whether%20the%20post%20is%20critical%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20winnability%20factor.%20For%20example%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdalveer-bhandari-icj%5C%22%3Enominated%20Justice%20Dalvir%20Bhandari%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20re-election%20to%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20despite%20there%20being%20another%20regional%20candidate%20running%20for%20the%20same%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20still%20decides%20to%20compete%2C%20then%20it%20requires%20the%20experience%20of%20senior%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20election%20officers%20at%20the%20mission%20to%20adeptly%20navigate%20regional%20dynamics%20and%20secure%20enough%20votes%20through%20personal%20appeals%20and%20reciprocal%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seasoned%20diplomat%20usually%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20better%20to%20undercount%20votes%2C%20as%20assurances%20are%20often%20given%20out%20but%20not%20acted%20upon.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20assurances%20are%20asked%20for%20in%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conservative%20approach%20means%20that%20India%20has%20fared%20exceptionally%20well%20at%20elections%20at%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20senior%20diplomat%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20India%20has%20seen%20a%20flawless%20record%20in%20successfully%20contesting%20elections%20in%20New%20York%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20November%2024%20election%2C%20India%20had%20last%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray%20for%20a%20UN%20post%20when%20it%20contested%20for%20one%20of%20the%20two%20seats%20allocated%20to%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Group%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-elected-to-un-statistical-commission-for-four-year-period%2Farticleshow%2F99292363.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20UN%20Statistical%20Commission%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20competition%20included%20China%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20South%20Korea.%20Indian%20officials%20considered%20the%20winning%20tally%20of%2046%20to%2053%20as%20a%20significant%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReal%20loss%20over%20symbolic%20post%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20the%20posts%20of%20vice-chairs%20at%20UN%20bodies%20are%20usually%20nominal.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unesco.org%2Fen%2Fexecutive-board%2Fbrief%5C%22%3Estated%20role%20of%20the%20UNESCO%20Executive%20Board%20vice%20chairs%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20administer%20a%20session%2C%20by%20rotation%2C%20during%20the%20chairman%E2%80%99s%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20their%20largely%20symbolic%20role%2C%20sources%20explained%20that%20elections%20for%20vice-chair%20posts%20are%20hardly%20contested%20as%20regional%20groups%20generally%20come%20to%20an%20understanding%20over%20a%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20obviously%20not%20the%20case%20in%20the%20election%20held%20during%20218th%C2%A0session%20of%20the%20UNESCO%E2%80%99s%20executive%20board%20on%20November%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20response%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20when%20asked%20for%20comment%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20at%20the%20UNESCO%20election%20to%20Pakistan.%20On%20his%20Twitter%20account%2C%20Sharma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FVishalVSharma7%2Fstatus%2F1728735243216228522%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Erecently%20highlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%20has%20been%20elected%20as%20the%20year-long%20chair%20of%20UNESCO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhc.unesco.org%2Fen%2Fcommittee%5C%22%3EWorld%20Heritage%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20World%20Heritage%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindutva%20apparatchik%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%202020%2C%20Sharma%20was%20a%20largely%20unknown%20figure%20outside%20the%20BJP%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20little%20there%20is%20suggests%20his%20ambassadorial%20appointment%20to%20UNESCO%20is%20perhaps%20linked%20to%20his%20%E2%80%98cultural%20nationalism%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C5th%20August%20is%20a%20civilisational%20day%2C%20greater%20than%20perhaps%20even%20the%20transfer%20of%20political%20power%20on%2015%20Aug%2C%20because%20on%205th%20Aug%2C%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20Indian%20civilization%E2%80%99s%20independence%20will%20be%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVishalVSharma01%2Fstatus%2F1290129811835215874%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%20on%20the%20day%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20laid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%2C%20somewhat%20ironically%20%E2%80%93%20given%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20being%20built%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20which%20Hindutva%20activists%20had%20destroyed%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%20of%20tolerance%20%26amp%3B%20Raghupati%20Raja%2C%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20over%20the%20evil%20of%20extremism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20that%20tweet%2C%20he%20was%20named%20to%20the%20prestigious%20ambassadorial%20post%20at%20UNESCO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701400419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01084217%2FVishal-Sharma-UNESCO.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funesco-election-india-pakistan-vishal-v-sharma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20magnitude%20of%20the%20margin%20is%20conspicuous%2C%20given%20India's%20historical%20success%20in%20securing%20positions%20when%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20roles%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20other%20multilateral%20entities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funesco-election-india-pakistan-vishal-v-sharma%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEveryone%20Says%20Dhoni%20Is%20Best%20Captain%2C%20But%20Rohit...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashwin%20Hits%20Bullseye%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20remain%20absent%20from%20the%20national%20T20I%20side%20and%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20break%20from%20the%20ODI%20format%20for%20the%20series%20against%20South%20Africa.%20As%20fans%20remain%20hopeful%20of%20his%20return%20to%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20there%20have%20been%20talks%20around%20his%20continuity%20as%20India's%20skipper.%20Though%20India%20failed%20to%20win%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20under%20Rohit's%20leadership%2C%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20hosts%20was%20far%20from%20a%20disappointing%20one.%20But%2C%20it's%20also%20true%20that%20after%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20no%20other%20Indian%20skipper%20has%20managed%20to%20crack%20the%20ICC%20code%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20veteran%20spinner%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20analysing%20Rohit%20as%20a%20captain%2C%20a%20cricketer%20and%20a%20person%2C%20gave%20the%20most%20apt%20explanation%20of%20the%20respect%20the%20India%20skipper%20has%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20take%20a%20look%20at%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20everybody%20will%20be%20telling%20you%20that%20MS%20Dhoni%20is%20the%20best%20captain.%20(But)%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20an%20outstanding%20person%2C%20(and)%20he%20understands%20every%20single%20player%20in%20the%20team.%20He%20knows%20the%20likes%20and%20dislikes%20of%20each%20of%20us%20and%20has%20a%20great%20understanding.%20He%20puts%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20know%20each%20player%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20in%20a%20video%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20walked%20the%20talk%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20giving%20India%20splendid%20starts%20at%20the%20top%20in%20almost%20every%20match%2C%20including%20the%20final.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Australian%20team%20that%20emerged%20triumphant%20in%20the%20summit%20clash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20talks%20about%20Ashwin%20getting%20the%20nod%20in%20the%20final%20but%20that%20didn't%20happen.%20The%20veteran%20off-spinner%2C%20however%2C%20was%20prepared%20to%20even%20cheer%20for%20the%20team%20from%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I%20playing%20the%20final%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20team%20combination%20and%20all%20is%20secondary.%20Firstly%2C%20it's%20about%20empathy%2C%20(and)%20I%20keep%20stressing%20it%20a%20lot.%20It's%20like%20standing%20in%20someone%20else's%20shoes%20and%20looking%20at%20things%20from%20his%2Fher%20perspective.%20Had%20I%20been%20in%20Rohit's%20shoes%2C%20I%20would%20have%20thought%20100%20times%20about%20altering%20the%20(winning)%20combination.%20It%20was%20going%20alright%20for%20the%20team%2C%20so%20why%20rest%20a%20fast%20bowler%20for%20three%20spinners%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20understood%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20thought%20process.%20Playing%20the%20final%20is%20big%2C%20(and)%20I%20was%20preparing%20for%20three%20days%20in%20the%20lead-up.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20also%20prepared%20to%20cheer%20for%20the%20side%20and%20run%20in%20with%20energy%20drinks%20if%20I%20was%20not%20given%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20was%20mentally%20prepared%20for%20that%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20concluded.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701400320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fsk1hl7sg_rohit-and-dhoni-bcci_625x300_01_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Feveryone-will-tell-you-ms-dhoni-is-best-captain-but-rohit-sharma-is-r-ashwin-hits-bullseye-4623095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20summed%20up%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20cri