rily%20make%20checking%20a%20potential%20partner's%20Instagram%20followers%20an%20immediate%20priority%20while%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20actively%20thought%20of%20doing%20that%20unless%20I%20saw%20some%20kind%20of%20red%20flag%20on%20the%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20I%20was%20on%20a%20date%20with%20someone%20and%20they%20said%20something%20that%20kind%20of%20set%20off%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20something%20weirdly%20misogynistic%20or%20making%20light%20of%20porn%20addiction%20%E2%80%94%20that%20might%20be%20a%20clue%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Anderson%2C%20the%20men's%20dating%20coach%2C%20said%20that%20most%20women%20she%20knows%20don't%20%26quot%3Bproactively%20examine%26quot%3B%20who%20guys%20are%20following%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20strikes%20me%20as%20a%20little%20neurotic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20men%20should%20be%20more%20mindful%20about%20how%20they%20present%20themselves%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-app-tips-tinder-match-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20as%20they%20would%20in%20person%2C%20especially%20if%20they're%20trying%20to%20secure%20dates%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20absolutely%20recommend%20single%20guys%20unfollow%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fonlyfans-sex-workers-escorts-porn-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOnlyFans%3C%2Fa%3E%20models%20or%20other%20thirsty%20content%20they're%20following%20on%20Instagram%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20clarified%20that%20spending%20money%20and%20time%2C%20for%20example%2C%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-see-increased-in-revenue-profit-creators-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOnlyFans%20subscriptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20counterprodu