Cp%3EThe%20film%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BLove%20Has%20Won%3A%20The%20Cult%20of%20Mother%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20tracks%20the%20ascension%20of%20Amy%20Carlson%20as%20a%20guru.%20The%20group%20espoused%20both%20New%20Age%20and%20QAnon-adjacent%20beliefs%20and%20alternative%20health%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20leading%20followers%20online%20and%20living%20with%20a%20smaller%20group%20of%20devotees%20in%20Colorado%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20Oregon%2C%20Carlson's%20mummified%20body%20was%20discovered%20by%20police%20in%202021.%20Her%20followers%20had%20been%20keeping%20a%20vigil%20over%20it%20for%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20cult%2C%20and%20where%20it%20stands%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20was%20the%20'Mother%20God'%20cult%2C%20'Love%20Has%20Won%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20left%20her%20job%20as%20a%20McDonald's%20manager%20in%20the%20late%202000s%2C%20and%20began%20posting%20videos%20online%20as%20Mother%20God%20with%20%3Cspan%3EAmerith%20White%20Eagle%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20man%20she%20dubbed%20to%20as%20Father%20God.%20He%20was%20the%20first%20man%20who%20would%20accompany%20her%20and%20bear%20the%20title%2C%20but%20there%20would%20be%20several%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20moved%20on%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2F2023%2F11%2Flove-has-won-mother-god-cult-amy-carlson%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20building%20a%20following%20online%20on%20Facebook%20and%20YouTube.%20Hannah%20Olson%2C%20the%20director%20of%20%26quot%3BLove%20Has%20Won%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20the%20group%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20attracted%20followers%20who%20had%20undergone%20difficulties%20in%20the%20American%20health%20system%3A%20in%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20early%20members%20of%20the%20group%20claimed%20that%20Carlson%20had%20cured%20his%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside