ter%20-%20Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHenry%20Kissinger's%20death%20has%20led%20some%20lawmakers%20to%20air%20critiques%20of%20his%20record.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20long%20been%20closely%20associated%20with%20excesses%20of%20US%20foreign%20policy%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20understood%20why%20people%20revered%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20House%20Democrat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20when%20a%20former%20leading%20statesman%20dies%2C%20members%20of%20Congress%20only%20offer%20glowing%20tributes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Henry%20Kissinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20much%20about%20Kissinger%20that%20I've%20heard%20that%20I%20think%20is%20particularly%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Greg%20Casar%20of%20Texas%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-santos-expulsion-exclusive-perks-congress-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeath%20at%20the%20age%20of%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20spurred%20yet%20another%20round%20of%20reflections%20on%20Kissinger's%20legacy%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20intertwined%20with%20the%20height%20of%20America's%20Cold%20War%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKissinger%2C%20who%20served%20as%20both%20the%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20and%20secretary%20of%20state%20under%20Republican%20Presidents%20Richard%20Nixon%20and%20Gerald%20Ford%2C%20has%20been%20lauded%20for%20his%20effectiveness%20in%20opening%20up%20relations%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20and%20pursuing%20a%20policy%20of%20detente%20with%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20foreign%20policy%20decisions%20that%20hurt%20and%20killed%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20including%20supporting%20repressive%20right-wing%20regimes%20in%20Latin%20America%20an