5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%2C%20activists%20and%20scientists%20have%20noted%20that%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%20is%20a%20crucial%20one%20in%20several%20aspects.%20Soaring%20temperatures%20broke%20world%20records%20this%20year.%20The%20COP%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20setting%20new%20actions%20towards%20limiting%20global%20warming%20to%20under%201.5%C2%B0C%20when%20compared%20to%20pre-industrial%20levels%2C%20including%20discussing%20actions%20based%20on%20the%20results%20of%20the%20first%20Global%20Stocktake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20including%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%93%20which%20have%20fewer%20economic%20and%20technical%20resources%20to%20deal%20with%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20impacts%20and%20have%20contributed%20lesser%20than%20developed%20countries%20have%20to%20climate%20change%20%E2%80%93%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20changing%20weather%2C%20including%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20intense%20bouts%20of%20rainfall%2C%20floods%20and%20droughts.%20A%20decision%20on%20the%20details%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20include%20funds%20from%20developed%20countries%20to%20implement%20adaptation%20and%20mitigation%20measures%20to%20tackle%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%20in%20least-developed%20and%20developing%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20taken%20at%20this%20COP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20first%20day%20of%20COP28%20was%20witness%20to%20the%20formal%20announcement%20of%20this%20fund.%20Several%20countries%20including%20Japan%20and%20Germany%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20fund%20already%2C%20which%20has%20received%20pledges%20of%20more%20than%20US%24400%20million%20so%20far.%20India%20inaugurated%20its%20COP28%20pavilion%20on%20the%20first%20day.%20A%20report%20released%20by%20the%20World%20Meteorological%20Organisation%20on%20November%2030%20revealed%20that%202023%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20warmest%20year%20ever%2C%20and%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20have%20been%20the%20warmest%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20the%20formal%20announcement%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20is%20good%20news%2C%20COP28%20has%20already%20been%20marred%20by%20numerous%20controversies%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20CEO%20of%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Abu%20Dhabi%20National%20Oil%20Company%20(ADNOC)%20as%20the%20president%20designate%20of%20the%20COP%2C%20and%20reports%20of%20UAE%20using%20their%20position%20as%20host%20of%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%20to%20further%20fossil%20fuel%20extraction%20in%20several%20countries.%20The%20COP28%20president%2C%20however%2C%20has%20refuted%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECOP28%20kicks%20off%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UN%20Framework%20Convention%20for%20Climate%20Change%E2%80%99s%20(UNFCCC)%20annual%20Conference%20of%20Parties%2C%20or%20the%20COP%2C%20is%20where%20world%20leaders%20and%20country%20representatives%20discuss%2C%20negotiate%20and%20decide%20on%20the%20actions%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20tackle%20climate%20change%20and%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%C2%B0C%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20of%202015.%20The%2028th%20edition%20of%20the%20COP%20kicked%20off%20on%20November%2030%20at%20Dubai%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20Around%20180%20heads%20of%20states%2C%20world%20leaders%20and%20government%20representatives%20will%20take%20part%20in%20COP28%2C%20including%20India%E2%80%99s%20union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Nearly%201%2C00%2C000%20delegates%20are%20registered%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20and%20around%204%2C00%2C000%20visitors%20are%20expected%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%20zone%E2%80%9D%20area%20of%20business%20and%20technology%20exhibitions%20adjoining%20the%20summit%2C%20per%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fnov%2F29%2Fcop28-president-denies-on-eve-of-summit-he-abused-his-position-to-sign-oil-deals%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20An%20estimated%20170%20%E2%80%98agenda%20items%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20across%20multiple%20negotiation%20tracks%20and%20discussions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%20will%20be%20a%20particularly%20crucial%20one%2C%20experts%20have%20stressed.%20Soaring%20temperatures%2C%20which%20experts%20attribute%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20broke%20world%20records%20this%20year.%20The%20current%20year%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F2023-on-track-to-become-hottest%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eset%20to%20be%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20hottest%20year%20on%20record.%20Global%20warming%20has%20also%20resulted%20in%20more%20changes%20in%20weather%20patterns%2C%20and%20more%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20intense%20bouts%20of%20rainfall%2C%20floods%20and%20droughts.%20The%20time%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20is%20right%20here%2C%20and%20right%20now%2C%20experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Furgent-need-for-higher-climate-action-to-limit-global-warming-unep-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estressed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20COP28%2C%20therefore%2C%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20setting%20new%20actions%20towards%20this%20goal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Furgent-need-for-higher-climate-action-to-limit-global-warming-unep-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2021%20about%20how%20a%20recent%20analysis%20by%20the%20UN%20%E2%80%93%20the%20UN%20Emissions%20Gap%20Report%20%E2%80%93%20has%20estimated%20that%20the%20world%20will%20need%20to%20cut%20emissions%20by%2028%25%20by%202030%20to%20achieve%20the%20goal%20of%20limiting%20warming%20to%202%C2%B0C%20as%20per%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20and%20by%2042%25%20to%20achieve%20the%201.5%C2%B0C%20goal.%20Drastic%20steps%20will%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20achieve%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimon%20Steill%2C%20executive%20secretary%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20in%20his%20opening%20speech%20at%20the%20plenary%20talks%20of%20COP28%20on%20November%2030%20said%20that%20we%20are%20taking%20%E2%80%9Cbaby%20steps%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStepping%20far%20too%20slowly%20from%20an%20unstable%20world%20that%20lacks%20resilience%2C%20to%20working%20out%20the%20best%20responses%20to%20the%20complex%20impacts%20we%20are%20facing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20teach%20climate%20action%20to%20run.%20Because%20this%20has%20been%20the%20hottest%20year%20ever%20for%20humanity.%20So%20many%20terrifying%20records%20were%20broken.%20We%20are%20paying%20with%20peoples%E2%80%99%20lives%20and%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20teach%20climate%20action%20to%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonstiell%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40SimonStiell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNFCCC%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNFCCC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Executive%20Secretary%2C%20during%20the%20Opening%20Plenary%20of%20COP28%2C%20reiterating%20the%20need%20to%20accelerate%20climate%20action.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCOP28%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23COP28%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUniteActDeliver%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UniteActDeliver%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyQYaZ6OQ8u%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FyQYaZ6OQ8u%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20COP28%20UAE%20(%40COP28_UAE)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCOP28_UAE%2Fstatus%2F1730258387399590074%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELoss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20is%20formally%20approved%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20huge%20victory%20for%20small%20island%20states%20and%20developing%20and%20least-developed%20countries%2C%20the%20first%20day%20of%20COP28%20witnessed%20the%20formal%20approval%20of%20the%20financial%20mechanisms%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20countries%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change%20that%20has%20caused%20impacts%20including%20numerous%20changes%20in%20weather%20patterns.%20Many%20in%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20including%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20are%20witnessing%20an%20increasing%20number%20and%20intensity%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20intense%20bouts%20of%20rainfall%2C%20floods%20and%20heat%20waves.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20total%20GDP%20loss%20to%20India%20in%202022%20is%20around%208%25%20compared%20to%20a%20world%20without%20climate%20change%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1AeDfbnEBaXql6gGl88A-yw0JUTWyBFIqeGMOlyDS6X8%2Fedit%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20new%20report%20released%20today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Delaware%20that%20analysed%20the%20estimated%20current%20GDP%20and%20capital%20wealth%20losses%20from%20climate%20change.%20As%20of%202022%2C%20India%20has%20also%20suffered%20a%20cumulative%20decrease%20of%207.9%25%20in%20capital%20wealth%2C%20mostly%20due%20to%20climate%20impacts%20to%20human-produced%20capital%20(such%20as%20on%20infrastructure).%20Including%20GDP%20and%20capital%20effects%20over%2030%20years%20since%201992%20(the%20Rio%20Convention)%2C%20the%20total%20economic%20loss%20is%20estimated%20at%20USD%203%2C555%20billion.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20climate%20change%20has%20already%20caused%20a%20global%20loss%20of%201.8%25%20of%20GDP%2C%20or%20USD%201.5%20trillion%2C%20in%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20some%20of%20these%20losses%20caused%20by%20climate%20change%20are%20tangible%2C%20many%20others%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20mental%20health%20repercussions%20caused%20by%20peoples%E2%80%99%20migrations%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20events%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not.%20Many%20of%20these%20countries%20which%20are%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%20have%20also%20contributed%20far%20lesser%20than%20developed%20countries%20have%20to%20historical%20greenhouse%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20developing%20countries%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20in%20responding%20to%20economic%20and%20non-%20economic%20loss%20and%20damage%20associated%20with%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20including%20extreme%20weather%20events%20and%20slow%20onset%20events%E2%80%9D%20can%20directly%20access%20resources%20from%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund%2C%20countries%20agreed%20on%20Day%20One%20of%20COP28%2C%20as%20listed%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fresource%2Fcp2023_L1_cma2023_L1_adv.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUNFCCC%20document%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Fund%20will%20be%20serviced%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%2C%20dedicated%20and%20independent%20secretariat%E2%80%9D%20and%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20for%20a%20period%20of%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20be%20governed%20and%20supervised%20by%20a%20Board%20(which%20will%20be%20the%20decision-making%20body)%20of%2026%20members%20including%2012%20members%20from%20developed%20countries%2C%20three%20members%20from%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20states%20and%20one%20member%20from%20a%20developing%20country%20that%20is%20not%20part%20of%20some%20of%20the%20categories%20mentioned%20in%20the%20list.%20Observers%20will%20also%20be%20permitted%20to%20attend%20the%20Fund%E2%80%99s%20meetings%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20develop%20and%20carry%20out%20an%20observer%20accreditation%20process%2C%20per%20the%20document.%20Funds%20will%20be%20operated%20through%20a%20resource%20allocation%20system%20that%20prioritises%20the%20needs%20of%20developing%20countries%20that%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20accounts%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20impacts%20of%20climate%20events%20%E2%80%9Crelative%20to%20national%20circumstances%E2%80%9D.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20a%20minimum%20percentage%20allocation%20floor%20for%20the%20least%20developed%20countries%20and%20small%20island%20developing%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20several%20nations%20including%20Japan%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20have%20pledged%20more%20than%20400%20million%20in%20total%20to%20the%20Fund%20and%20more%20is%20expected%2C%20said%20COP28%20president%20Al-Jaber.%20The%20threshold%20to%20operationalise%20the%20fund%20was%20USD%20200%20million%2C%20but%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Creached%20north%20of%20%24400%20and%20more%20in%20the%20coming%20days%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20moment%20Parties%20collectively%20agreed%20to%20operationalize%20Loss%20and%20Damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20%24420%20million%20was%20pledged%2C%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20the%20decision%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20collective%20political%20will%20to%20support%20those%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fw6r97qc9SO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fw6r97qc9SO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20COP28%20UAE%20(%40COP28_UAE)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCOP28_UAE%2Fstatus%2F1730265461047087401%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Presidency%E2%80%99s%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20translating%20visions%20and%20aspirations%20into%20real%20practical%20actions%20that%20will%20make%20a%20difference.%20Next%20is%20the%20realisation%20of%20the%20GST%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGetting%20this%20done%20and%20over%20the%20line%20is%20a%20clear%20demonstration%20of%20our%20determination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Al-Jaber%20added.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20commit%20we%20deliver%20and%20that%20will%20be%20the%20DNA%20of%20COP28.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20hard%20fought%20historic%20agreement%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Avinash%20Persaud%2C%20developing%20country%20negotiator%20and%20special%20climate%20envoy%20to%20Barbados%20and%20PM%20Mia%20Mottley.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20recognition%20that%20climate%20loss%20and%20damage%20is%20not%20a%20distant%20risk%20but%20part%20of%20the%20lived%20reality%20of%20almost%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20that%20money%20is%20needed%20to%20reconstruct%20and%20rehabilitate%20if%20we%20are%20not%20to%20let%20the%20climate%20crisis%20reverse%20decades%20of%20development%20in%20mere%20moments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbyadavbjp%2Fstatus%2F1730215705633751548%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DvqtpLTbqF8SPMCvqYAO_5g%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20%E2%80%9Coperationalisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%20signal%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Clandmark%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20positive%20signal%20of%20momentum%20from%20COP28%20in%20UAE%20on%20the%20first%20day%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbyadavbjp%2Fstatus%2F1730215705633751548%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DvqtpLTbqF8SPMCvqYAO_5g%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CLandmark%20decision%20on%20operationalisation%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20was%20adopted%20in%20the%20opening%20plenary%20of%20COP28.%20India%20strongly%20supports%20the%20decision%20to%20operationalise%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20positive%20signal%20of%20momentum%20from%20COP28%20in%20UAE%20on%20the%20first%20day%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELandmark%20decision%20on%20operationalisation%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20was%20adopted%20in%20the%20opening%20plenary%20of%20COP28.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20strongly%20supports%20the%20decision%20to%20operationalise%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJqpEXVsTC4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJqpEXVsTC4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20(%40byadavbjp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbyadavbjp%2Fstatus%2F1730215705633751548%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20amid%20the%20historic%20decision%20to%20operationalise%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20within%20a%20year%20of%20its%20establishment%2C%20addressing%20underlying%20concerns%20becomes%20critical%2C%20commented%20Harjeet%20Singh%2C%20head%20of%20global%20political%20strategy%20at%20Climate%20Action%20Network.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20one%20hand%2C%20rich%20countries%20have%20pushed%20for%20the%20World%20Bank%20to%20host%20this%20Fund%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20ensuring%20a%20speedy%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CConversely%2C%20they%20have%20attempted%20to%20dilute%20their%20financial%20obligations%20and%20resisted%20defining%20a%20clear%20finance%20mobilisation%20scale%E2%80%A6The%20absence%20of%20a%20defined%20replenishment%20cycle%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20Fund%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20sustainability.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20robust%20system%2C%20particularly%20integrated%20with%20the%20Global%20Stocktake%20process%20and%20the%20new%20climate%20finance%20goal%2C%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20that%20COP28%20results%20in%20a%20meaningful%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAffluent%20nations%20must%20meet%20their%20financial%20obligations%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmanner%20proportionate%20to%20their%20role%20in%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20which%20has%20been%20primarily%20driven%20by%20decades%20of%20unrestrained%20fossil%20fuel%20consumption%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20climate%20finance%20delivered%20to%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELast%20nine%20years%20have%20been%20the%20warmest%20ever%3A%20WMO%20report%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20World%20Meteorological%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwmo.int%2Fnews%2Fmedia-centre%2F2023-shatters-climate-records-major-impacts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprovisional%20State%20of%20the%20Global%20Climate%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20published%20on%20November%2030%20to%20inform%20negotiations%20at%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20confirmed%20that%202023%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20warmest%20year%20on%20record.%20Data%20until%20the%20end%20of%20October%20shows%20that%20the%20year%20was%20about%201.4%20Degrees%20Celsius%20above%20the%20pre-industrial%201850-1900%20baseline%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20past%20nine%20years%20%E2%80%93%202015%20to%202023%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20the%20warmest%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGreenhouse%20gas%20levels%20are%20record%20high.%20Global%20temperatures%20are%20record%20high.%20Sea%20level%20rise%20is%20record%20high.%20Antarctic%20sea%20ice%20is%20record%20low.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20deafening%20cacophony%20of%20broken%20records%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20WMO%20Secretary-General%20Prof.%20Petteri%20Taalas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202023%20WMO%20report%20rings%20a%20dire%20warning%20for%20India%2C%20underlining%20the%20stark%20reality%20of%20a%20planet%20in%20crisis%2C%20said%20Anjal%20Prakash%2C%20Clinical%20Associate%20Professor%20(Research)%20and%20Research%20Director%2C%20Bharti%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Policy%2C%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20and%20an%20IPCC%20author.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnprecedented%20heatwaves%2C%20soaring%20greenhouse%20gas%20levels%2C%20and%20alarming%20declines%20in%20Antarctic%20Sea%20ice%20demand%20urgent%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20faces%20severe%20repercussions%20as%20rising%20temperatures%20exacerbate%20heatwaves%2C%20impacting%20agriculture%2C%20water%20resources%2C%20and%20public%20health.%20The%20heightened%20risk%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20floods%2C%20and%20cyclones%20poses%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20vulnerable%20communities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20approach%20COP28%2C%20India%20stands%20at%20a%20crossroads%20where%20immediate%20and%20decisive%20actions%2C%20including%20ramping%20up%20renewable%20energy%2C%20are%20imperative%20to%20safeguard%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20future%2C%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThe%201.5-degree%20limit%20remains%20achievable%2C%20provided%20leaders%20prioritise%20sustainable%20policies%20over%20short-term%20gains.%20Let%20this%20report%20serve%20as%20a%20call%20to%20action%20for%20India%20and%20the%20world%2C%20recognising%20that%20the%20choices%20we%20make%20today%20will%20determine%20the%20well-being%20of%20generations%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%20and%20COP28%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20inaugurated%20its%20COP28%20pavilion%20on%20November%2030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20keeping%20with%20our%20civilisational%20ethos%2C%20India%20has%20always%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20climate%20action%20even%20as%20we%20pursue%20social%20and%20economic%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1981197%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2030%2C%20just%20before%20setting%20off%20to%20attend%20COP28.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELeaving%20for%20Dubai%2C%20where%20I%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20COP-28%20Summit.%20This%20forum%20will%20witness%20important%20deliberations%20to%20strengthen%20the%20efforts%20to%20overcome%20climate%20change%20and%20further%20sustainable%20development.%20I%20will%20also%20be%20interacting%20with%20various%20world%20leaders%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1730222162588631463%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20our%20G20%20Presidency%2C%20climate%20was%20high%20on%20our%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20includes%20numerous%20concrete%20steps%20on%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainable%20development.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20COP-28%20taking%20forward%20the%20consensus%20on%20these%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20leaders%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20%E2%80%93%20which%20India%20hosted%20in%20September%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20several%20aspects%20of%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECOP28%20will%20also%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20review%20progress%20made%20under%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20and%20chart%20a%20path%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfuture%20course%20on%20climate%20action%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20in%20his%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20Voice%20of%20Global%20South%20Summit%20convened%20by%20India%2C%20the%20Global%20South%20spoke%20for%20the%20need%20for%20climate%20action%20based%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20equity%2C%20climate%20justice%2C%20and%20common%20but%20differentiated%20responsibilities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20greater%20focus%20on%20adaptation.%20It%20is%20important%20that%20efforts%20of%20the%20developing%20world%20be%20supported%20with%20adequate%20climate%20financing%20and%20technology%20transfer.%20They%20must%20have%20access%20to%20equitable%20carbon%20and%20development%20space%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20COPs%2C%20health%20is%20on%20the%20agenda.%20An%20entire%20day%20%E2%80%93%20December%203%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20dedicated%20to%20discussions%20on%20health%20alone.%20However%2C%20while%2070%20countries%20are%20sending%20their%20ministers%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20communication%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20yet%20on%20whether%20India%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20will%20be%20at%20this%20crucial%20meeting%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F29%2Fcop28-india-not-sending-delegation-to-crucial-climate-health-meet-in-dubai-on-december-3-2637279.html%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20t%3Cspan%3Ehe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20expects%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20roadmap%E2%80%9D%20on%20climate%20finance%20at%20the%20ongoing%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said%20on%20November%2030%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Findia-expects-clear-roadmap-on-climate-finance-during-cop28-foreign-secretary-kwatra%2F1865755%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECOP28%3A%20Already%20mired%20in%20controversy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2028th%20annual%20climate%20change%20conference%2C%20however%2C%20is%20already%20mired%20in%20controversy%2C%20as%20reports%20reveal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20Sultan%20Ahmed%20Al-Jaber%20as%20the%20president-designate%20of%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%20raised%20heavy%20criticism.%20Al%20Jaber%20is%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Minister%20of%20Industry%20and%20Advanced%20Technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20CEO%20of%20ADNOC%2C%20the%20Abu%20Dhabi%20National%20Oil%20Company.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1613482020583378945%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20the%20move%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20problematic%E2%80%9D%20and%20have%20criticised%20the%20appointment%20saying%20it%20is%20in%20direct%20conflict%20of%20interest%20to%20the%2