nteers%20to%20share%20the%20load.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Vatsala%20feels%20fulfilled%20looking%20back%20at%20a%20life%20of%20service%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20dedication%20to%20his%20family%20and%20business.%20He%20finds%20joy%20in%20having%20transformed%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20business%20into%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20keep%20%E2%80%98Babu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20running%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20him%20here%3A%20%2B91%2098863%2075522.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700833878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20in%20Halaguru%20village%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Babu%20Hotel%20has%20served%20chiblu%20idlis%20made%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20for%20over%20seven%20decades.%20Its%20owner%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20shares%20what%20makes%20these%20idlis%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334919%2Fchiblu-idlis-in-bamboo-bengaluru-babu-hotel-halaguru-village-in-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Freed%20from%20captivity%3A%20The%2079%20Israeli%20hostages%20released%20by%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700830260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-israel-hostages_6378069.jpg%3F20231130225026%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-are-the-first-71-israeli-hostages-released-by-hamas-13015007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20more%20Israeli%20hostages%20were%20freed%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Thursday%20as%20part%20of%20a%20string%20of%20releases%20under%20a%20temporary%20ceasefire%20deal.%22%